warning_dialog.title: 경고
warning_dialog.warning:
Before using Maid Fiddler, understand that this tool can destroy your save if you are not careful!

Make sure that
  1. You make a backup of your save file
  2. You don't use Maid Fiddler during the intro (first three in-game days)
  3. You understand that using Maid Fiddler can cause the game to skip story, softlock or even crash

By clicking OK you accept that you understand all this.
